validationRule.title: Vehicle position outside agency coverage area
validationRule.errorDescription: The vehicle position should be inside the agency coverage area.  This is defined as within roughly 1/8 of a mile (200 meters) of the GTFS shapes.txt data, or stops.txt locations if the GTFS feed doesn't include shapes.txt.

validationRule.title: GTFS-rt content changed but has the same header timestamp
validationRule.errorDescription: The GTFS-rt header timestamp value should always change if the feed contents change - the feed contents must not change without updating the header timestamp
validationRule.occurrenceSuffix: was the same for this and the previous feed iteration but the feed content was not the same

validationRule.title: GTFS-rt trip_id does not exist in GTFS data and does not have schedule_relationship of ADDED
validationRule.errorDescription: All trip_ids provided in the GTFS-rt feed must exist in the GTFS data, unless the schedule_relationship is ADDED
validationRule.occurrenceSuffix: does not exist in the GTFS data and does not have schedule_relationship of ADDED

validationRule.title: GTFS-rt route_id does not exist in GTFS data
validationRule.errorDescription: All route_ids provided in the GTFS-rt feed must exist in the GTFS data
validationRule.occurrenceSuffix: does not exist in the GTFS data routes.txt

validationRule.title: schedule_relationship not populated
validationRule.errorDescription: trip.schedule_relationship and stop_time_update.schedule_relationship should be populated
